# ADVANCED PRICE IMPORTER 2.0 – AI PROCUREMENT & PRICE INTELLIGENCE CENTER

## Objective

Transform this page from a simple document uploader into a complete supplier price intelligence workflow.

The goal is not only to import prices.

The goal is to:

- Compare supplier prices
- Detect price increases and decreases
- Update product costs automatically
- Recalculate margins automatically
- Generate purchasing recommendations
- Detect better suppliers
- Synchronize approved prices with Zoho Books
- Maintain full historical price tracking

The page must be optimized for both desktop and mobile.

